# Debug Bridge reference

**Port `8735`**, debug builds only, code in **`app/src/debug/`**. Detailed verification steps: **`debug-bridge-verify.mdc`**, **`debug-bridge-test-procedures.mdc`**.

## Port forward

```bash
adb -s emulator-5554 forward tcp:8735 tcp:8735
```

Use `adb devices` for the real serial (emulator vs phone).

## Deploy targets

**Emulator (preferred)** — Pixel7 AVD from `setup-env.sh`:

```bash
emulator -avd Pixel7 &
adb wait-for-device && gradle installDebug && adb -s emulator-5554 shell am start -n com.realmsoffate.game/.MainActivity
adb -s emulator-5554 forward tcp:8735 tcp:8735
```

**Physical phone (Galaxy S23)** — user `phone` fish function: wireless ADB + deploy + launch. Forward **`tcp:8735`** to the device serial. LAN `192.168.68.64`; if wireless port changes, reconnect with `adb connect 192.168.68.64:<port>`.

## Logs

```bash
adb -s emulator-5554 logcat -s RealmsDebug:V
```

## In-app AI / state dump

**More → Debug** dumps state + AI log. Pull via user’s **`pulldebug`** → **`debug-dumps/`** (gitignored). Newest:

```bash
ls -t debug-dumps/debug_*.txt 2>/dev/null | head -1
```

## HTTP API (sketch)

| Area | Paths |
|------|--------|
| State | `GET /state`, `/state/diff`, `/state/overlay` |
| Visual | `GET /screenshot`, `/screenshot/both`, `/describe`, `/describe/ui`, `/describe/annotated` |
| Commands | `POST /input`, `/confirm`, `/cancel`, `/navigate`, `/tap` |
| Theme | `POST /theme`, `/font-scale` |
| Inject | `POST /inject`, `/inject/messages`, `/inject/reset` |
| Macros | `POST /macro/new-game`, `/macro/advance`, `/macro/death`, `/macro/simulate-gameplay` |

## Fish helper (`debug`)

```
debug state | diff | overlay | screenshot | describe
debug input <text> | confirm | cancel | navigate <screen> | tap <label>
debug theme <light|dark|system> | font-scale <n>
debug inject <field> <value> | reset
debug new-game | death | advance [n]
debug events
```
